Jonathan Hansler https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Hansler 0 Jonathan Hansler (born John Hansler Brittan) is an English actor. He trained at the Studio 68 of Theatre Arts, graduating in 1985. He has since worked extensively in theatre, film and television. Jonathan_Hansler ( born John_Hansler_Brittan ) is an_English_actor .
